Individual




Bruce L. Claflin



Mr. Bruce L. Claflin is Independent Director at IDEXX Laboratories, Inc., Independent Director at Ciena Corp., Independent Director at Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. and President & Director at Kids First (Virgin Islands). He is on the Board of Directors at IDEXX Laboratories, Inc., Ciena Corp., Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. and Kids First (Virgin Islands). Mr. Claflin was previously employed as President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by 3Com Corp., President by 3Com Ventures, Inc., Senior Vice President, GM-Sales & Marketing by Digital Equipment Corp., General Manager-Products & Brand Management by International Business Machines Corp., and President by IBM PC Co. He also served on the board at IBM Credit LLC, TheServerSide Communities and tw telecom, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Pennsylvania State University.



